description:
Retrieves all Fixed Prices on a price table or trade policy. 

## Response body example

```json
[
    {
        "tradePolicyId": "6",
        "value": 20.9,
        "listPrice": 22.9,
        "minQuantity": 1,
        "dateRange": {
            "from": "2021-12-30T22:00:00-03:00",
            "to": "2021-12-30T22:00:00-04:00"
        }
    },
    {
        "tradePolicyId": "1",
        "value": 18.9,
        "listPrice": null,
        "minQuantity": 1
    }
]
```
